data.description: When you step into this meticulously maintained home you will see it's ready for you to move-in. With the kitchen being the heart of the home, it features a large island with seating for 4. Espresso cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances give a dramatic showing. An inviting morning room is surrounded with windows and is open to the kitchen and family room which has a gas fireplace and has surround sound. The 5 bedrooms include a 1st floor bedroom with a private full bath located behind the family room and garage. The primary bedroom private bath has double closets, double sinks, and double shower heads. There is a media room fully wired with surround sound and ready for an overhead projector or could be 6th bedroom. The garage walls have been finished with drywall and painted. Plus the garage floor has an epoxy coating. The tankless hot water heater is not only energy efficient but has hot water ready in an instant. Home has a security system.
